An AI assistant that generates multiple AWS architecture options from a single project requirement â€” along with trade-offs on cost, performance, scalability, and resilience.

ğŸ” Problem Statement
Cloud solutioning often focuses on a single design path â€” but in reality, every architecture has trade-offs. For developers and architects working under time pressure (e.g., hackathons, MVPs, PoCs), it's hard to evaluate multiple AWS designs quickly and choose the best fit for their goals and constraints.

ğŸ’¡ What ArchWise Does
Accepts high-level requirements (e.g., â€œreal-time API with low latency and high availabilityâ€)

Generates 2â€“3 alternative AWS architectures for the use case

